' changelog: CHANGELOG_212
' description: Claude 流式 tok/s 估算 tick 从 SDK stream_event 到 renderer 展示的 sequence
' last_updated: 2026-06-04
@startuml token-rate-live-flow

actor "Claude Agent SDK" as Sdk
participant "sdk-message-translate" as Translate
participant "live-token-rate" as LiveRate
participant "eventBus" as Bus
participant "bootstrap-wiring" as Bootstrap
participant "preload eventsApi" as Preload
participant "useTokenRatesPoll" as Hook
participant "token-usage-store" as Store
participant "HeaderTokenRates / DataPanel" as Ui
database "token_usage" as Db

Sdk -> Translate: stream_event(content_block_delta)
Translate -> LiveRate: handleStreamEventForLiveRate(sessionId, msg, now)
LiveRate -> LiveRate: estimate tokens from text/thinking delta
LiveRate -> Bus: emit('token-rate-tick', {sessionId,bucketKey,tps,ts})
note right of LiveRate
  Tick is display-only.
  Estimated token/s never writes token_usage
  and never enters AgentEvent ingest.
end note
Bus -> Bootstrap: token-rate-tick
Bootstrap -> Preload: safeSend(IpcEvent.TokenRateTick, payload)
Preload -> Hook: onTokenRateTick(callback)
Hook -> Store: applyLiveTick(payload)
Store -> Ui: fresh liveBySession snapshot
Ui -> Ui: rank by current tok/s

Sdk -> Translate: result(modelUsage)
Translate -> Bus: token-usage-changed after token_usage insert
Translate -> LiveRate: clearLiveTokenEstimate(sessionId)
LiveRate -> Bus: emit done tick(tps=0, done=true)
Bus -> Bootstrap: token-usage-changed
Bootstrap -> Preload: safeSend(IpcEvent.TokenUsageChanged, payload)
Hook -> Db: tokenUsageRates()/tokenUsageTopToday()
Db --> Hook: 60s window exact output totals
Hook -> Store: setRates()/setTopToday()
Store -> Ui: exact window value replaces stale estimate

note bottom
  Codex has turn.completed usage only in current app path.
  It keeps the existing 60s poll path until reliable text or usage deltas are wired.
end note

@enduml
